'''2016年巴林大獎賽'''（{{lang-en|2016 Bahrain Grand Prix}}），官方名稱為'''2016年一級方程式賽車海灣航空巴林大獎賽'''（{{lang-en|2016 Formula 1 Gulf Air Bahrain Grand Prix}}）<ref name="official">{{cite web|title=2016 Formula 1 Gulf Air Bahrain Grand Prix|url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/races/2016/Bahrain.html|work=formula1.com|publisher=[[Formula_One_Group|Formula One Administration]]|accessdate=2016-04-01|archive-date=2016-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401173433/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/races/2016/Bahrain.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是2016年4月3日舉辦於[[巴林|巴林]]的一場[[一級方程式賽車|一級方程式賽車]]賽事。比賽在[[巴林國際賽道|巴林國際賽道]]進行，總計57圈。這是[[2016年世界一級方程式錦標賽|2016年世界一級方程式錦標賽]]的第2場分站賽事，<ref name="calendar">{{cite web |url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/12/f1-2016-calendar-confirmed.html |title=FIA confirms 2016 calendar |work=Formula1.com |publisher=Formula One Management |date=2015-12-02 |accessdate=2015-12-02 |archive-date=2015-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151203231526/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2015/12/f1-2016-calendar-confirmed.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>同時也是第12屆[[巴林大獎賽|巴林大獎賽]]。[[路易斯·漢米爾頓|路易斯·漢米爾頓]]是這場分站的衛冕冠軍，其隊友[[尼可·羅斯堡|尼可·羅斯堡]]以積分領先之姿來到此站。

漢米爾頓在二度受到嚴厲批評的「淘汰制」排位賽取得[[桿位|桿位]]，領先羅斯堡與[[法拉利車隊|法拉利]]的[[賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾|賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾]]。最終，羅斯堡贏得分站冠軍，[[奇米·雷克南|奇米·雷克南]]與漢米爾頓分別取得亞軍及季軍。

==賽事簡報==

===背景===
[[2016年澳洲大獎賽|澳洲分站]]的「淘汰制」排位賽遭到廣泛批評後，各車隊投票表決廢止現行的制度，改回{{F1|2006}}至{{F1|2015}}的排位賽系統。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Morlidge |first1=Matthew |title=New qualifying format slammed as 'unacceptable' and 'embarrassing' |url=http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10210796/new-qualifying-format-slammed-as-unacceptable-and-embarrassing |publisher=Sky Sports |accessdate=2016-03-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319081208/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10210796/new-qualifying-format-slammed-as-unacceptable-and-embarrassing |archivedate=2016-03-19 |date=2016-03-19 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Benson |first=Andrew |title=Lewis Hamilton on pole position in Australia after new F1 qualifying |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/35850356 |accessdate=2016-03-19 |work=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |date=2016-03-19 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319084216/http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/35850356 |archivedate=2016-03-19 |location=[[Melbourne|Melbourne]] |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Johnson|first=Daniel|title=Bernie Ecclestone vows to scrap new Formula One qualifying system after Australian Grand Prix farce|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2016/03/19/australian-grand-prix-qualifying-farce-as-lewis-hamilton-takes-p/|accessdate=2016-03-19|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|publisher=[[Telegraph_Media_Group|Telegraph Media Group]]|date=2016-03-19|location=[[Melbourne|Melbourne]]|archive-date=2016-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319111446/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2016/03/19/australian-grand-prix-qualifying-farce-as-lewis-hamilton-takes-p/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Freeman|first1=Glenn|last2=Parkes|first2=Ian|title=Bernie Ecclestone declares F1's new qualifying format 'pretty crap'|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123341/ecclestone-declares-new-qualifying-crap|website=Autosport.com|publisher=Haymarket Media Group|accessdate=2016-03-19|date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2016-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160327192559/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123341/ecclestone-declares-new-qualifying-crap|dead-url=yes}}</ref>然而，在該分站當週，策略工作小組對此事正式投票，選擇在巴林大獎賽保留目前的「淘汰制」，並在下一站[[2016年中國大獎賽|中國]]前徹底審查。<ref>{{cite web|first=Ian|last=Parkes|title=F1 gives elimination qualifying system reprieve for the Bahrain GP|url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123446/elimination-qualifying-to-stay-for-bahrain|date=2016-03-24|work=Autosport.com|publisher=Haymarket Media Group|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160325135801/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123446/elimination-qualifying-to-stay-for-bahrain|archive-date=2016-03-25|accessdate=2016-04-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>據後來的報導，車隊只能在淘汰制與2016年前及現行淘汰的混合制兩者間進行抉擇，徹底回歸到2006至2015年間賽制的決議從未被討論過。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Galloway |first1=James |last2=Morlidge |first2=Matthew |title=F1 qualifying: Why do elimination rules remain for Bahrain GP? |url=http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10221833/f1-qualifying-why-do-elimination-rules-remain-for-bahrain-gp |publisher=Sky Sports |accessdate=2016-04-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401144320/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10221833/f1-qualifying-why-do-elimination-rules-remain-for-bahrain-gp |archivedate=2016-04-01 |date=2016-03-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>[[梅賽德斯車隊|梅賽德斯]]的賽車運動總監{{le|托托·沃爾夫|Toto Wolff}}仍舊堅持認為目前的賽制需要改變，表示他並不期望排位賽能夠比兩週前變得更加具有趣味性。<ref>{{cite news |title=F1’s new qualifying format will flop again in Bahrain, says Toto Wolff |url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/mar/29/f1-bahrain-grand-prix-new-qualifying-format-toto-wolff-mercedes |accessdate=2016-03-20 |work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] |agency=[[Reuters|Reuters]] |publisher=Guardian Media Group |date=2016-03-29 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330140906/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/mar/29/f1-bahrain-grand-prix-new-qualifying-format-toto-wolff-mercedes |archivedate=2016-03-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>車手們對於維持目前賽制表示批評，[[法拉利車隊|法拉利]]的[[賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾|賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾]]向記者表示「他與任何他認識的人一樣失望」，<ref>{{cite web |last1=Baldwin |first1=Alan |title=Vettel in less than fine fettle over qualifying |url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-motor-f1-bahrain-qualifying-idUKKCN0WX28I |publisher=Reuters |accessdate=2016-04-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401085731/http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-motor-f1-bahrain-qualifying-idUKKCN0WX28I |archivedate=2016-04-01 |date=2016-03-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>梅賽德斯車手[[路易斯·漢米爾頓|路易斯·漢米爾頓]]表示「特別重要的是因為車迷們已經感到不滿」，稱這項決議相當「奇怪」。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Benson |first1=Andrew |title=Lewis Hamilton says it is strange that qualifying is unchanged at Bahrain GP |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/35937850 |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2016-04-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401085905/http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/35937850 |archivedate=2016-04-01 |date=2016-03-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>另外，正賽當日安排了一場會議，由包括[[國際汽車聯盟|國際汽聯]]主席[[尚·陶德|尚·陶德]]、一級方程式賽車商業權持有者[[伯尼·埃克萊斯頓|伯尼·埃克萊斯頓]]等人出席討論排位賽之進行方式。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Cooper |first1=Adam |title=Ecclestone and Todt to attend second F1 qualifying summit on Sunday |url=http://www.foxsports.com/motor/story/f1-qualifying-bahrain-meeting-bernie-ecclestone-jean-todt-033116 |publisher=[[Fox_Sports|Fox Sports]] |accessdate=2016-04-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402120404/http://www.foxsports.com/motor/story/f1-qualifying-bahrain-meeting-bernie-ecclestone-jean-todt-033116 |archivedate=2016-04-02 |date=2016-03-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

在澳洲大獎賽與[[伊斯班·古鐵雷斯|伊斯班·古鐵雷斯]]發生碰撞之後，[[費爾南多·阿隆索|費爾南多·阿隆索]]因為肋骨骨折及[[氣胸|氣胸]]，被排除於這場分站，由麥拉倫儲備車手[[斯托弗·范多恩|斯托弗·范多恩]]頂替上場。<ref>{{cite web |last=Pablo |first=Elizalde |title=Alonso will not race in the Bahrain GP |url=http://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/alonso-will-not-race-in-the-bahrain-gp-683160/ |website=Motorsport.com |publisher=Motorsport Network, LLC. |accessdate=2016-03-31 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160331120221/http://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/alonso-will-not-race-in-the-bahrain-gp-683160/ |archivedate=2016-03-31 |date=2016-03-31 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>[[哈斯車隊|哈斯]]認為古鐵雷斯原先的底盤受到嚴重撞擊，以至於無法順利修復，因而替他換上了新的底盤。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Zimmermann |first1=Ruben |title=Haas in Bahrain: Neues Chassis für Esteban Gutierrez |url=http://www.motorsport-total.com/f1/news/2016/03/haas-in-bahrain-neues-chassis-fuer-esteban-gutierrez-16032805.html |website=motorsport-total.com |accessdate=2016-03-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330160615/http://www.motorsport-total.com/f1/news/2016/03/haas-in-bahrain-neues-chassis-fuer-esteban-gutierrez-16032805.html |archivedate=2016-03-30 |date=2016-03-28 |language=de |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=Bahrain Grand Prix: Fernando Alonso to use new power unit |url=http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/35919470 |accessdate=2016-03-29 |work=[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]] |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |date=2016-03-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330160357/http://www.bbc.com/sport/formula1/35919470 |archivedate=2016-03-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>另外，即使[[奇米·雷克南|奇米·雷克南]]的引擎在澳洲因渦輪增壓器故障起火，[[法拉利車隊|法拉利]]仍舊在此站將它修復完成。多虧車隊當場立即的處理，防止了內燃機損壞，他們在巴林分站僅需更換渦輪。<ref>{{cite web |last=Barretto |first=Lawrence |title=Quick response saved Raikkonen's Ferrari F1 engine in Australia |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123500/quick-response-saved-raikkonen-engine |work=Autosport.com |publisher=Haymarket Media Group |accessdate=2016-03-30 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160330140425/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123500/quick-response-saved-raikkonen-engine |archivedate=2016-03-30 |date=2016-03-30 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>{{le|小阿方索·塞利斯|Alfonso Celis Jr.}}首度登上一級方程式賽車賽場，他在第一階段練習賽時，為[[印度威力車隊|印度威力]]試車。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Parkes |first1=Ian |title=Alfonso Celis Jr gets F1 practice run in Bahrain with Force India |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123438/ |accessdate=2016-03-31 |6= |website=Autosport.com |publisher=Haymarket Media Group |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160331172713/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123438/ |archivedate=2016-03-31 |date=2016-03-24 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

[[一級方程式輪胎|輪胎]]供應商[[倍耐力|倍耐力]]為巴林站帶來的三種配方，供車手們自由選擇。這三種配方分別為超軟胎、軟胎及中性胎，與前一站澳洲相同。積分領先的梅賽德斯與法拉利在輪胎分配方面採取了不同的策略，梅賽德斯僅為他們的車手各準備一套中性胎，而法拉利則以軟胎最為代價，各配置了三套中性胎。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Freeman |first1=Glenn |title=Mercedes and Ferrari take different F1 tyre splits for Bahrain GP |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123411 |work=Autosport.com |publisher=Haymarket Media Group |accessdate=2016-04-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401172624/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123411 |archivedate=2016-04-01 |date=2016-03-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Pirelli reveal driver tyre choices for Bahrain |url=https://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2016/3/pirelli-reveal-driver-tyre-choices-for-bahrain.html |website=formula1.com |publisher=ormula One World Championship Limited |accessdate=2016-04-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401172633/https://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/latest/headlines/2016/3/pirelli-reveal-driver-tyre-choices-for-bahrain.html |archivedate=2016-04-01 |date=2016-03-22 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

與往年一樣，這場比賽伴隨著有關{{le|巴林人權|Human rights in Bahrain|巴林人權局勢}}的議題。巴林人權及民主學院（{{lang|en|Bahrain Institute for Rights and Democracy}}）在比賽週之前，寫了一封公開信給尚·陶德，指出「國際汽聯授權的這場比賽期間已經嚴重侵犯人權」，並且強烈要求這項運動的管理機構應「準備好在未來幾年內取消這場賽事」。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Weaver |first1=Paul |title=Bahrain Institute raises concerns of human rights abuse with FIA |url=http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/apr/03/bahrain-institute-for-rights-democracy-letter-fia-human-rights-abuse |publisher=''[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]'' |accessdate=2016-04-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160405090909/http://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/apr/03/bahrain-institute-for-rights-democracy-letter-fia-human-rights-abuse |archivedate=2016-04-05 |date=2016-04-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

===自由練習賽===
根據{{F1|2016}}賽季的規則，將舉行三階段自由練習賽，週五有兩場長一個半小時，而剩餘的一場一小時練習賽則位在週六排位賽之前。<ref name="pracreg">{{cite web |title=Practice and qualifying |url=http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/inside-f1/rules-regs/Practice_qualifying_and_race_start_procedure.html |website=formula1.com |publisher=Formula One World Championship Limited |accessdate=2016-03-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160318130826/http://www.formula1.com/content/fom-website/en/championship/inside-f1/rules-regs/Practice_qualifying_and_race_start_procedure.html |archivedate=2016-03-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>週五的第一階段練習賽期間，梅賽德斯寫下的時間與其主要對手有著明顯的差距。[[尼可·羅斯堡|尼可·羅斯堡]]以1:32.292拿下全場最快圈速，較位居第二的隊友路易斯·漢米爾頓快上約半秒。第三快的奇米·雷克南與羅斯堡有著將近2秒的差距。首度登場的斯托弗·范多恩及小阿方索·塞利斯分別取得第18與第21名，皆較其各自的隊友來的慢。<ref name="fp1">{{cite web |last1=Parkes |first1=Ian |title=Nico Rosberg leads Mercedes one two in first F1 practice in Bahrain |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123532/rosberg-leads-mercedes-onetwo-in-practice |work=Autosport.com |publisher=Haymarket Media Group |accessdate=2016-04-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401170914/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123532/rosberg-leads-mercedes-onetwo-in-practice |archivedate=2016-04-01 |date=2016-04-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>塞利斯於3號彎衝出賽道，迫使他得減慢速度以免車輛受到傷害，因為他最大的責任是替車隊收集資訊。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Parkes |first1=Ian |title=Hairy moment spooked Celis into backing off on F1 GP practice debut |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123535/hairy-moment-spooked-celis-on-debut |work=Autosport.com |publisher=Haymarket Media Group |accessdate=2016-04-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402114240/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123535/hairy-moment-spooked-celis-on-debut |archivedate=2016-04-02 |date=2016-04-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>此階段的天氣異常地涼爽，預期與週日在晚間舉行的正賽是有相近的天氣狀況。因此，許多車隊決定讓他們的車輛在場上多跑幾圈，其中共有16位車手跑超過20圈。<ref name="fp1"/>

羅斯堡在週五下午的第二階段練習賽再度成為場上最快車手。他的1:31.001單圈時間較[[2015年巴林大獎賽|去年比賽]]的[[桿位|桿位]]成績快上1.5秒。路易斯·漢米爾頓以落後羅斯堡0.241秒的成績名列第二。[[詹森·巴頓|詹森·巴頓]]為麥拉倫取得第三，但他的時間仍落後第一名超過1秒。<ref name="fp2">{{cite web |last1=Barretto |first1=Lawrence |title=Nico Rosberg on top again in second Bahrain Grand Prix practice |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123538/rosberg-on-top-again-in-practice-two |work=Autosport.com |publisher=Haymarket Media Group |accessdate=2016-04-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401170851/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123538/rosberg-on-top-again-in-practice-two |archivedate=2016-04-01 |date=2016-04-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>幾位車手表示對麥拉倫在週五練習賽期間的速度感到驚訝，巴頓更形容這是該隊「近幾年來」的最佳狀態。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Anderson |first1=Ben |last2=Adam |first2=Mitchell |title=McLaren pace surge in Bahrain GP practice surprises its F1 rivals |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123546/mclaren-pace-surge-surprises-rivals |work=Autosport.com |publisher=Haymarket Media Group |accessdate=2016-04-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402114646/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123546/mclaren-pace-surge-surprises-rivals |archivedate=2016-04-02 |date=2016-04-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>[[馬克斯·維斯塔潘|馬克斯·維斯塔潘]]位居第四，緊追在後的是雷克南與維泰爾兩位法拉利車手。維泰爾在使用軟胎時曾寫下第三快的成績，但在換上超軟胎後出現幾次失誤，意味著他最終無法取得比第六名更佳的成績。當他的左後車輪螺母縮脫後，迫使他在練習賽結束前15分鐘提前收場。范多恩在第二階段名列第11，而在塞利斯下場後的[[塞吉歐·培瑞茲|塞吉歐·培瑞茲]]則取得第15名，領先其隊友[[尼可·賀根堡|尼可·賀根堡]]兩名。<ref name="fp2"/>[[羅曼·格羅斯讓|羅曼·格羅斯讓]]的車輛壓過路緣石時出現震動，造成他的前鼻翼斷裂，也使他脫離了賽道。之後，他順利回到維修站並更換了鼻翼。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Zakkar |first1=Oubay |last2=Adam |first2=Mitchell |title=Vibrations over kerbs caused Haas wing trouble in Bahrain practice |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123549/kerb-vibrations-caused-haas-wing-trouble |work=Autosport.com |publisher=Haymarket Media Group |accessdate=2016-04-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402114126/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123549/kerb-vibrations-caused-haas-wing-trouble |archivedate=2016-04-02 |date=2016-04-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>此階段練習賽結束後，[[雷諾車隊|雷諾]]的[[凱文·馬格努森|凱文·馬格努森]]未進行過磅檢查，反而將他的車輛駛回車庫，並進行維修工作。因此，他在正賽時必須從維修道發車。<ref name=magnussen>{{cite web |last1=Parkes |first1=Ian |title=Renault's Kevin Magnussen hit with pitlane start for Bahrain GP |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123547/magnussen-hit-with-pitlane-start |work=Autosport.com |publisher=Haymarket Media Group |accessdate=2016-04-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402115011/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123547/magnussen-hit-with-pitlane-start |archivedate=2016-04-02 |date=2016-04-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

兩位法拉利車手在第三階段占據了一、二名，賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾寫下1:31.683的最快單圈成績，而奇米·雷克南則位居第二。羅斯堡與漢米爾頓兩位車梅賽德斯車手位居其後，在後方的則是[[維爾特利·鮑達斯|維爾特利·鮑達斯]]及羅曼·格羅斯讓。兩位梅賽德斯車手用上軟胎時，曾寫下相近的時間，但在羅斯堡換上超軟胎後，超越了漢米爾頓。午後陽光的高溫意味著此時的單圈時間會較第二階段下滑。[[威廉斯車隊|威廉斯]]的[[費利佩·馬薩|費利佩·馬薩]]換上全新且較短的鼻翼，但僅取得第九名，較其隊友鮑答斯慢上約半秒。紅牛二隊未用上超軟胎，兩位車手分別位居第15、16名。[[喬里昂·帕爾默|喬里昂·帕爾默]]取得第20名，但在練習賽結束前刺破了他的輪胎。<ref name="fp3">{{cite web |last1=Anderson |first1=Ben |title=Vettel fastest as Ferrari moves ahead in Bahrain GP practice three |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123566/vettel-fastest-as-ferrari-moves-ahead |work=Autosport.com |publisher=Haymarket Media Group |accessdate=2016-04-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402145347/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123566/vettel-fastest-as-ferrari-moves-ahead |archivedate=2016-04-02 |date=2016-04-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

===排位賽===
週六排位賽依舊維持以2016年的「淘汰制」規則進行。正如多年來一般，排位賽程序劃分為三個部分，第一階段（Q1）長16分鐘，而第二、第三階段（Q2、Q3）分別長15及14分鐘。所有22輛車在一階段上場，隨著前兩階段分各自淘汰7名車手後，剩餘的8位車手進入Q3爭奪桿位。然而，依據新的排位賽規則，在Q1經過7分鐘、Q2經過6分鐘及Q3第五分鐘後，開始以每90秒依序淘汰場上最慢的一位車手。<ref name=pracreg/>

Q1展開，所有車手上場跑出他們的最快時間，接著前段的車手回到了維修道，獨留將被淘汰的車手在場上爭奪。[[費利佩·納斯爾|費利佩·納斯爾]]與[[里奧·哈里恩多|里奧·哈里恩多]]皆無法做出他們的第二次單圈時間，其中，前者在他的首圈發生失誤，使他的排位敬陪末座。喬里昂·帕爾默在第二圈提高了他的時間，但他很快地就被寫下更快成績的斯托弗·范多恩擠下，被迫淘汰。[[帕斯卡·維爾莱茵|帕斯卡·維爾莱茵]]取得第16位，領先印度威力的塞吉歐·培瑞茲。凱文·馬格努森位居第19，但他因為受罰仍需從維修道起跑。<ref name="qualf1fan">{{cite web |last1=Collantine |first1=Keith |title=Hamilton claims pole with “sexy” record-breaking lap |url=http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2016/04/02/hamilton-claims-pole-sexy-record-breaking-lap/ |publisher=F1Fanatic |accessdate=2016-04-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160402162915/http://www.f1fanatic.co.uk/2016/04/02/hamilton-claims-pole-sexy-record-breaking-lap/ |archivedate=2016-04-02 |date=2016-04-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

第二階段排位賽在時間倒數下展開，但因為維修道末端的紅燈亮起，開始程序出現了問題，車手們被迫停止車輛。隨後，一位工作人員揮舞綠旗，指示車手可以回到賽場。<ref name=motorsportcom>{{cite web |last1=Elizalde |first1=Pablo |title=Bahrain GP: Hamilton on pole as qualifying disappoints again |url=http://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/bahrain-gp-hamilton-on-pole-as-qualifying-disappoints-again-683973/ |website=motorsport.com |accessdate=2016-04-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403120455/http://www.motorsport.com/f1/news/bahrain-gp-hamilton-on-pole-as-qualifying-disappoints-again-683973/ |archivedate=2016-04-03 |date=2016-04-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>此階段練習賽期間，路易斯·漢米爾頓寫下最快單圈時間，維泰爾也在羅斯堡出現失誤的情況下，取得第二名。[[丹尼爾·科維亞特|丹尼爾·科維亞特]]率先被淘汰，巴頓也在其初登場的隊友范多恩之前被出局。尼可·賀根堡是唯一一位回到場上刷新時間的車手，擠下格羅斯讓、[[馬克斯·維斯塔潘|馬克斯·維斯塔潘]]與[[小卡洛斯·塞恩斯|小卡洛斯·塞恩斯]]，順利以第八名晉身Q3。<ref name="qualf1fan"/>

當前段的車手在Q3做出他們的首次時間時，漢米爾頓卻在最後一彎發生失誤，使他落後隊友羅斯堡與兩位法拉利車手。賀根堡、兩位威廉斯車手及里卡多未再多做一次時間，先後被淘汰，而剩餘的四位車手則再度上場。漢米爾頓以1:29.493寫下巴林賽道史上最快的單圈時間，以0.077秒的些微之差，從隊友羅斯堡手中奪下桿位。維泰爾則以約半秒之差取得第3位，隊友雷克南位居第4。排位賽後，國際汽聯對漢米爾頓在維修道的倒車行為展開調查，使他的桿位受到威脅。最終，漢米爾頓遭到一次訓誡，桿位得以保住。<ref name="qualf1fan"/><ref>{{cite news |last=Lines |first=Chris |title=Hamilton edges Rosberg to take pole position at Bahrain GP |url=http://racing.ap.org/node/291604 |accessdate=2016-04-02 |work=Associated Press |agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |publisher=AP Sports |date=2016-04-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403111245/http://racing.ap.org/node/291604 |archivedate=2016-04-03 |location=Sakhir |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

====排位賽後====
許多評論家對此次排位賽的反應就如兩周前一般，不斷批評著這項新制。<ref name=motorsportcom/><ref name="skyquali">{{cite web |last1=Morlidge |first1=Matthew |title=2016 Bahrain Grand Prix: Conclusions from qualifying |url=http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10227136/2016-bahrain-grand-prix-conclusions-from-qualifying |publisher=Sky Sports |accessdate=2016-04-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403120953/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10227136/2016-bahrain-grand-prix-conclusions-from-qualifying |archivedate=2016-04-03 |date=2016-04-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>然而，國際汽聯、[[一級方程式集團|一級方程式管理公司]]（FOM）及各車隊在週日正賽當天進行的一場會議，對恢復至舊制排位賽未能達成共識，國際汽聯及FOM的代表更將這項選擇排除在外。各車隊也提出了所有車手在每個排位賽階段皆要跑出兩次時間的新提案。再將兩次時間加總以決定排位。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Barretto |first1=Lawrence |title=F1 fails to agree qualifying system change, rules out 2015 format |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123599/f1-fails-to-agree-on-qualifying-change |work=Autosport.com |publisher=Haymarket Media Group |accessdate=2016-04-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160403121155/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123599/f1-fails-to-agree-on-qualifying-change |archivedate=2016-04-03 |date=2016-04-03 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="vettelquali">{{cite web |last1=Galloway |first1=James |title=Sebastian Vettel hits out at aggregate qualifying proposal |url=http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10229727/sebastian-vettel-hits-out-at-aggregate-qualifying-proposal |publisher=Sky Sports |accessdate=2016-04-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408082049/http://www.skysports.com/f1/news/12433/10229727/sebastian-vettel-hits-out-at-aggregate-qualifying-proposal |archivedate=2016-04-08 |date=2016-04-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>各界對此的看法兩極。賽巴斯蒂安·維泰爾形容這是一個「胡鬧的理念」，丹尼爾·里卡多表示他「對此不很感興趣」，詹森·巴頓認為這是比目前的淘汰制更好的計畫。<ref name="vettelquali"/>不過，11支車隊在賽後的週四聯名上書，再度要求國際汽聯及FOM恢復到2015的排位賽制。管理當局與商業權持有人皆對此表示認同，但尚未做出正式決定。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Parkes |first1=Ian |title=F1 reverts to old qualifying format from Chinese Grand Prix |url=http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123660/f1-old-qualifying-format-back-from-china |work=Autosport.com |publisher=Haymarket Media Group |accessdate=2016-04-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160408082632/http://www.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/123660/f1-old-qualifying-format-back-from-china |archivedate=2016-04-08 |date=2016-04-07 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>
